description:
DigiAgriApp is a software aimed at farmers and anyone with cultivated land DigiAgriApp is a Free and Open Source Software solution aimed at farmers and anyone with cultivated land. DigiAgriApp is able to save the operations carried out in the field and all the data from different devices (mobile phones, weather stations, remotes such as drones or satellites) in a capillary manner, from the field to the individual plant.
